channel.title: Deleting with command prompt
channel.description: im trying to delete a possible virus that downloaded(i scanned it with avg free version but i don't trust it). I tried just putting it in the recycling bin but it said that the (zipped) folder was being used by another program. So i went into the command prompt and used this "del C:\Documents and Settings\Adam\Desktop\JbFrACwby_Gnss_www.musicground.com.br_bapho" but it keeps saying it cannot find the path or something, but its the correct path. what do i do, im scared that im entirely fucked.
